@TraderForge.API_HostAddress = http://localhost:5116

GET {{TraderForge.API_HostAddress}}/weatherforecast/
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Market Prices via POST
POST http://localhost:5116/api/prices
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "symbols": [
    "BTCUSDT",
    "ETHUSDT",
    "SOLUSDT"
  ]
}
